FBIS4-66068 "drweu103_j_94004" FBIS-WEU-94-103 Daily Report 26 May 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Berlusconi Reassures Slovenia, Croatia on Borders Berlusconi Reassures Slovenia, Croatia on Borders LD2605221394 Rome RAI Due Television Network in Italian 2135 GMT 26 May 94 LD2605221394 Rome RAI Due Television Network Italian BFN [Text] Prime Minister Silvio Berlusconi sent a reassuring message to Slovenia and Croatia following the arguments over the Osimo Treaty and the borders with Italy. Berlusconi announced that Italy intended to strengthen relations with the two republics utilizing negotiations covering every topic.
